{"aitVersion":"3.2.4","fileVersion":5,"fileType":"test case","createDate":"2026-03-11T15:30:14.615Z","creator":"ajoost","dto":{"changeDate":"2026-02-23T09:29:20.319Z","creator":"vgeoffre","dbId":166,"released":false,"inspectionType":"FULL_AND_PARTIAL_TEST","revisionNr":0,"createDate":"2024-04-03T09:41:41.969Z","state":"ENABLED","testCaseId":145,"testSectionDTOList":[{"changeDate":"2026-02-23T09:29:20.319Z","descriptionGerman":"","dbId":6677,"released":false,"inspectionType":"FULL_AND_PARTIAL_TEST","createDate":"2024-04-03T09:42:03.900Z","state":"ENABLED","testElementDTOList":[],"title":"<!--(DescriptionHead)Check Alarm: High Volume","titleType":"STANDARD","parameters":{"parameters":[],"rows":[]}},{"changeDate":"2026-02-23T09:29:20.319Z","descriptionGerman":"","dbId":6678,"released":false,"inspectionType":"FULL_AND_PARTIAL_TEST","createDate":"2024-04-03T09:42:03.900Z","state":"ENABLED","testElementDTOList":[{"changeDate":"2026-02-23T09:29:20.319Z","elementId":1001,"factor":0,"isOnReport":true,"dbId":28387,"createDate":"2024-04-03T09:42:03.900Z","state":"ENABLED","structureId":1000,"targetRawValue":"--><h4>Check Apnea Backup</h4>\n<br>\n\nIn this test, the activation of the backup ventilation is tested. The test is \npassed, if:\n<ul>\n    <li>The Apnea-Backup-Alarm is pressent within 17 seconds after start of ventilation\n    </li>\n    <li>Within 30 seconds after the ASL switches to active breathing, DuoPAP is the \n        active mode on the ventilator.\n    </li>\n</ul>\n<br>\n\nThe sequence for this test is:\n<br><br>\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<strong>\n(ASL |1/2) -> (Setup) -> (Exec) -> (Evaluation |1/2) -> (ASL |2/2) -> (Evaluation |2/2) -> (CleanUp)\n</strong>\n</div>\n<br>\n<ul>\n\n    <li><strong>(ASL |1/2)-Block:</strong>       \n        Sets ASL resistance and compliance according to the product requirements. At this \n        stage, the ASL is passive.\n       </li>\n\n    <li><strong>(Setup)-Block:</strong>\n        Sets predefined values according to the product requirements.\n    </li>\n    \n    <li><strong>(Exec)-Block:</strong>\n        <ol>\n            <li>Starts ventilation</li>\n            <li>Waits for 15 seconds.</li>\n        </ol>\n    </li>\n\n    <li><strong>(Evaluation |1/2)-Block:</strong>\n        <ol>\n            <li>Asserts, that the ventilator activates the Backup-Mode within 2 seconds</li>\n            <Strong>Note: </Strong>The internal code for \"Apnea Ventilation\" is 280200043.\n        </ol>\n    </li>\n    <li><strong>(ASL |2/2)-Block:</strong>\n        Activates active breathing on the ASL.\n    </li>\n\n    <li><strong>(Evaluation)-Block:</strong>\n        <ol>\n            <li>Asserts, that the ventilator switches back to DuoPAP within 30 seconds after \n                the activation of the ASL.\n            </li>\n        </ol>\n    </li>\n\n    <li><strong>(CleanUp)-Block:</strong>\n        Stops ventilation\n    </li>\n\n</ul>\n<br><br>\n<br><!--","targetTolerance":null,"typeId":1002,"targetSelection":null,"invertResult":false}],"title":"(DescriptionBody)","titleType":"STANDARD","parameters":{"parameters":[],"rows":[]}},{"changeDate":"2026-02-23T09:29:20.319Z","descriptionGerman":"<h1>Description</h1>\n<h2>Procedure</h2>\n<h3>What's been meassured?</h3>\n<h3>How is it asserted?</h3>\n<h2>Changes from original PPL:</h2>","dbId":6679,"released":false,"inspectionType":"FULL_AND_PARTIAL_TEST","createDate":"2024-04-03T09:42:03.900Z","state":"ENABLED","testElementDTOList":[],"title":"Pressure Values: Tidal value and PEEP-->","titleType":"STANDARD","parameters":{"parameters":[],"rows":[]}},{"changeDate":"2026-02-23T09:29:20.319Z","descriptionGerman":"","dbId":6681,"released":false,"inspectionType":"FULL_AND_PARTIAL_TEST","createDate":"2024-04-03T09:42:03.900Z","state":"ENABLED","testElementDTOList":[],"title":"........General Setup","titleType":"STANDARD","parameters":{"parameters":[],"rows":[]}},{"changeDate":"2026-02-23T09:29:20.319Z","descriptionGerman":"","dbId":6682,"re